lyrics:
[Verse]
I met her at the fair, under those neon lights
Her hair was like gold, shining oh so bright
She tasted like sugar, spun in the air
Sweet cotton candy, with a smile so rare

[Chorus]
Oh sweet cotton candy, you're my sugary delight
Taking me to places, on this colorful night
Oh sweet cotton candy, won't you dance with me
Together we'll rock 'n' roll, set our spirits free
